title: Ep. #94 | Catching Up: DAVII
description:
Singer-songwriter DAVII is here to talk about his new music and hit collaborations with Heize ("Jenga," "You, Clouds, Rain"). Also on the show, Eric and DAVII compete against each other in a game of song association. Find out who wins!
